    "description": "Glide, collect nuts and slap birds in this small 3d adventure. Keep an eye out for mythical golden peanuts as you make your way through the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877560/extras/51e2819c51dff8d5055a4aae19ac4cb2.poster.avif?t=1724947530\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877560/extras/51e2819c51dff8d5055a4aae19ac4cb2.webm?t=1724947530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877560/extras/51e2819c51dff8d5055a4aae19ac4cb2.mp4?t=1724947530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Glide your way from island to island and choose your own route in a semi-open world.<br></li><li> Use your tail to slap mean birds, defeat weasels and defeat small, but fun bosses!<br></li><li> Break crates &amp; barrels, collect all nuts &amp; coins and find mythical golden peanuts. Then use your coins to unlock cool new outfits!<br></li><li> Meet helpful inhabitants of the various islands, they may be able to help Walter on his journey!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877560/extras/f897436bd00d3213124c4190488228c1.poster.avif?t=1724947530\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877560/extras/f897436bd00d3213124c4190488228c1.webm?t=1724947530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877560/extras/f897436bd00d3213124c4190488228c1.mp4?t=1724947530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
